---
description: Frontend standards for Vite + TypeScript
globs:
  - "web/**"
alwaysApply: false
---

- Use Vite 7 conventions; prefer ESM imports and `moduleResolution: bundler`.
- Keep UI logic testable; co-locate `.test.ts` with code.
- When generating code, add types at boundaries, avoid `any`, use `as const` for literals.
- Prefer absolute imports via `tsconfig` paths when appropriate.
